SPLOOFTROOPERS COLLECTION:
0042/1000

NFT Photo Collection curated by members of the photography chat known as SPLOOFTROOPERS. A "sploof" is a unique signature for signing contracts through photography by using the generated image to verify the photo for two or more parties. The sploof is ritually burned to seal the deal when all parties are in assent.
